    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty ride and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me over the years. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with a new owner today! It runs smoothly and looks great\u2014perfect for someone looking for a dependable car that still has plenty of life left in it. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
