    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride and it's ready for a brand new adventure. It\u2019s been super reliable and is in really solid shape, perfect for your daily commute or those fun weekend road trips! It's clean, runs like a dream, and I\u2019ve really taken care of it over the years. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 33500.0,
