    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust 2003 Porsche 911 Turbo, powered by the race-derived 3.6L Mezger flat-six. This example features a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a sophisticated all-wheel-drive system that ensures maximum traction under load. The forced induction system utilizes twin K17 turbochargers, providing a broad torque curve and linear power delivery. It has been fastidiously maintained with an eye toward performance, including a recent overhaul of the cooling system with pinned lines\u2014a critical reliability upgrade\u2014and a refreshed suspension featuring Bilstein dampers. While the exterior shows honest signs of use, the drivetrain remains exceptionally tight and the four-piston Brembo monoblock calipers offer consistent, fade-free braking. This is a driver-focused machine ready for immediate spirited use.",
